  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/35af41ae2cdec955f8709a7301dd364d.poster.avif?t=1731002133\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/35af41ae2cdec955f8709a7301dd364d.webm?t=1731002133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/35af41ae2cdec955f8709a7301dd364d.mp4?t=1731002133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEED DA KING!</strong><br>Workers throw crops into your picnic basket. You can click or automate to throw the food from the basket into Da King's mouth. When Da King eats, he will throw a coin into your piggy bank, and his belly will increase, granting you rewards along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/2f614e532b240fe228d736a7e7114fb6.poster.avif?t=1731002133\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/2f614e532b240fe228d736a7e7114fb6.webm?t=1731002133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/2f614e532b240fe228d736a7e7114fb6.mp4?t=1731002133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use different coins for various upgrades and to add more workers. The only limitations are either your time or your rig. How big can you grow Da Kings belly?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868380/extras/86380cce0abe26c23b288fadac8629e1.poster.avif?t=1731002133\" width=396 height=222 ><s